<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Desiring to be with Christ, &quot;Oh, when I shall see Jesus.&quot;</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nitak nanta fehna 'k o̱
 Yakni 'lʋppa issʋt,
 Ʋba aholitopa
 Ona la chi̱ hoh cho?
 Nitak nanta fehna 'k o̱,
 Chisʋs fehna hona.
 Ont pi̱sʋt, iba ta̱kla
 Binili la chi̱ cho?

[V2]
 Chisʋs aiasha mak o̱
 Ona li hokmʋto,
 Si achukma̱ka kʋt, peh
 Bilia ho oke.
 A̱ Mi̱ko Chisʋs ʋto
 Tikba hekʋt a̱yʋt
 Si anukfihinli hosh
 Yak ʋm ahanchishke.

[V3]
 &quot;Ik chi nukwiyo kashke;
 An tʋshka chia hʋt,
 Ʋm anumpa ha̱ kʋllot
 Ish a hikkiashke.&quot;
 Achi hoka, sa yimmit
 Anukchieto hosh
 Chisʋs a̱ Mi̱ko yoka
 Iakaiya la chi̱.

[V4]
 Chisʋs ʋba Mi̱ko ya̱
 Iakaiya li kʋt,
 A sʋlli hokmak heto
 Ʋm ʋlhpiesashke.
 An Chisʋs fehna hoka
 I̱ sa hofahya wa:
 Si okcha̱ya ta̱kla 'k osh
 Issa la he keyushke.

[V5]
 Chisʋs holitopa ma!
 Si okcha̱ya taklʋt
 Chim ai a̱hli la chi̱ ka
 Is si apelashke.</lyrics>
<title>Nitak nanta fehna 'k o̱ ƲIT60</title>
<time_sig>7.6.7.6.D</time_sig>
<hymn_number>60</hymn_number>
<author>Alfred Wright</author>
</song>